  ('FAR', 'Shareholders'' Equity & Share-Based Payment',
   'Share appreciation rights payable in cash are accounted for as:',
   'An equity-settled share-based payment measured at grant date only', 'An expense only when exercised', 'A memorandum entry until exercise', 'A liability remeasured at fair value at each reporting date until settlement, with changes recognized in profit or loss',
