   'P60,000', 'P120,000', 'P140,000', 'P150,000',
   2, 'The P200,000 realization loss is charged 50% to Jo: P240,000 − P100,000 = P140,000, which is the cash she receives.', 2),
  ('AFAR', 'Partnership Accounting',
