  ('AFAR', 'Partnership Accounting',
   'Partners Alma, Bert, Cita and Dina have capital balances of P400,000, P270,000, P160,000 and P121,000, and share profits 40%, 30%, 20% and 10%, respectively. In a cash priority program, the first cash available to partners goes to:',
   'Alma', 'Bert', 'Cita', 'Dina',
