  ('AUD', 'Auditing in an IT Environment',
   'An auditor reviews controls that govern who may log in to the financial reporting system and what data each user may access. These controls are best classified as:',
   'General controls over access security', 'Application input edit checks', 'Application output controls', 'Application processing controls',
   0, 'Logical access security restricting user authentication and authorization is a general IT control affecting the whole environment, not an application-specific edit check.', 1),
  ('AUD', 'Auditing in an IT Environment',
