   'P50,000', 'P100,000', 'P400,000', 'P500,000',
   3, 'A non-resident foreign corporation is subject to a 25% final tax on gross income from Philippine sources. P2,000,000 x 25% = P500,000, with no deductions allowed.', 1),
  ('TAX', 'Income Tax: Corporations',
   'A domestic corporation has net taxable income of P4,000,000 and total assets of P80,000,000 (excluding the land on which its office stands). Applying the two-condition test, the regular corporate income tax due is:',
   'P800,000', 'P1,000,000', 'P80,000', 'P200,000',
