  ('TAX', 'Income Tax: Corporations',
   'A proprietary educational institution has net income of P8,000,000, of which P2,000,000 (25% of total) comes from unrelated trade or business. Because unrelated income does not exceed 50% of total income, the income tax due is:',
   'P2,000,000', 'P160,000', 'P800,000', 'P1,600,000',
