   0, 'The GPP determines net income at the partnership level (itemized or OSD). Each partner reports his distributive share as part of gross income and cannot again deduct the expenses already claimed by the GPP.', 2),
  ('TAX', 'Income Tax: Partnerships, Estates & Trusts',
   'A joint venture formed for undertaking a construction project, where the co-venturers are licensed local contractors, is:',
