  ('RFBT', 'Credit Transactions: Pledge, Mortgage & Guaranty',
   'Ana is surety for Ben loan to Carlo. Carlo, without Ana consent, grants Ben an extension of time to pay. The effect on Ana is that she is:',
   'Still fully bound because sureties can never be released', 'Released from the suretyship by the extension granted without her consent', 'Bound only for half the obligation', 'Converted into a mere guarantor',
   1, 'An extension of time for payment granted by the creditor to the debtor without the consent of the surety extinguishes the suretyship, because it varies the obligation the surety agreed to answer for.', 2),
  ('RFBT', 'Credit Transactions: Pledge, Mortgage & Guaranty',
   'In antichresis, the creditor who receives the fruits of the debtor immovable must apply them:',
