   0, 'In antichresis the creditor acquires the right to receive the fruits of the immovable, obliged to apply them first to the interest, if owing, and thereafter to the principal of the credit.', 1),
  ('RFBT', 'Credit Transactions: Pledge, Mortgage & Guaranty',
