   1, 'An order to pay solely out of a particular fund makes the promise conditional and destroys negotiability; merely indicating the account to be debited or reimbursed, however, does not.', 3),
  ('RFBT', 'Negotiable Instruments',
   'A note promising to pay 50,000 pesos with interest at 12 percent per annum and 25 percent attorney fees in case of suit:',
